  "root_text": {
    "iti64:0.1": "Itivuttaka 64 ",
    "iti64:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti64:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti64:0.4": "Duccaritasutta ",
    "iti64:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti64:2.1": "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, duccaritāni. ",
    "iti64:2.2": "Katamāni tīṇi? ",
    "iti64:2.3": "Kāyaduccaritaṁ, vacīduccaritaṁ, manoduccaritaṁ—",
    "iti64:2.4": "imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi duccaritānī”ti. ",
    "iti64:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti64:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti64:3.1": "“Kāyaduccaritaṁ katvā, ",
    "iti64:3.2": "vacīduccaritāni ca; ",
    "iti64:3.3": "Manoduccaritaṁ katvā, ",
    "iti64:3.4": "yañcaññaṁ dosasaṁhitaṁ. ",
    "iti64:4.1": "Akatvā kusalaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "iti64:4.2": "katvānākusalaṁ bahuṁ; ",
    "iti64:4.3": "Kāyassa bhedā duppañño, ",
    "iti64:4.4": "nirayaṁ sopapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti64:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti64:5.2": "Pañcamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti64:0.1": "So It Was Said 64 ",
    "iti64:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti64:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti64:0.4": "Bad Conduct ",
    "iti64:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti64:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three kinds of bad conduct. ",
    "iti64:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti64:2.3": "Bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind. ",
    "iti64:2.4": "These are the three kinds of bad conduct.” ",
    "iti64:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti64:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti64:3.1": "“Having done bad things ",
    "iti64:3.2": "by way of body, ",
    "iti64:3.3": "speech, and mind, ",
    "iti64:3.4": "and whatever else is corrupt; ",
    "iti64:4.1": "not having done good deeds, ",
    "iti64:4.2": "and having done many bad, ",
    "iti64:4.3": "when their body breaks up, that witless person ",
    "iti64:4.4": "is reborn in hell.” ",
    "iti64:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
